query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from question AS q
inner join tag_question AS tq
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.score >= 1 AND q.score <= 10
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('stackoverflow')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('c++17',
'clang',
'css-animations',
'fork',
'internationalization',
'mobile',
'pytorch',
'row',
'rstudio',
'webserver',
'webview',
'windows');
